data.description: Did someone say open floor plan? This beautiful 4 bedroom home is located in the Griffin Park subdivision. Upon entering the home, you are greeted with a spacious family room leading into a kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances. The master bathroom features a double vanity and separate garden tub. The 3 additional bedrooms have large windows that provide you with an abundance of natural light. There is a covered patio in the backyard which provides the perfect entertainment space to host your Summertime barbecues. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
